      <title>以色列将在几天内应对伊朗潜在的直接袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/israel-bracing-for-potential-direct-attack-from-iran-in-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉西方情报评估的人士称，以色列正在准备应对伊朗可能直接或通过其代理人在几天内对政府目标发动的袭击，无人机和导弹将袭击政府目标，此举有可能引发全面的地区战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/israel-bracing-for-potential-direct-attack-from-iran-in-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
