      <title>德国极右翼支持在欧洲大选前减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/german-far-right-support-dwindles-ahead-of-european-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在六月的欧洲议会选举之前，德国选择党的支持率进一步下降，但总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨的三路执政联盟仍在努力从极右翼政党的困境中获得任何优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/german-far-right-support-dwindles-ahead-of-european-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反 LGBTQ 法案成为加纳选举的政治烫手山芋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/anti-lgbt-bill-becomes-political-hot-potato-for-ghana-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳的两位总统候选人谴责了同性恋，但没有表示他们是否会将一项严厉的反同性恋法案签署为法律，该法案可能会对国家财政产生严重影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/anti-lgbt-bill-becomes-political-hot-potato-for-ghana-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
