      <title>欧盟调查发现 Novo 的 Wegovy 并未增加自杀风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/eu-probe-finds-no-added-suicide-risk-linked-to-novo-s-wegovy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟药品监管机构发现，服用诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 的 Wegovy 和 Ozempic 等流行的新型减肥和糖尿病药物的人不会增加自杀或自残的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/eu-probe-finds-no-added-suicide-risk-linked-to-novo-s-wegovy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰财政部长敦促检察官调查奥伦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/polish-finance-minister-urges-prosecutors-to-scrutinize-orlen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰财政部长安杰伊·多曼斯基 (Andrzej Domanski) 周五表示，在国营 Orlen SA 能源集团支付 4 亿美元购买其从未收到的石油的消息曝光后，波兰国家检察官应该“彻底”调查该能源集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/polish-finance-minister-urges-prosecutors-to-scrutinize-orlen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
