      <title>对俄罗斯实施制裁后瑞士将举行中立投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/swiss-activists-get-enough-signatures-for-vote-on-neutrality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士决定就俄罗斯入侵乌克兰实施制裁，引发了一场辩论，瑞士即将就其长期中立性进行全民投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/swiss-activists-get-enough-signatures-for-vote-on-neutrality</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 05:41:42 GMT</pubDate>
